{"tid":519703,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(中伏)黎緊會去曼谷嘅要小心呢間夜市pad thai","createTime":"2018-01-04T15:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T10:53:06.000Z","uid":14722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db1f89e986cc4e66a522a5556b9f9dbeae492610","tid":519703,"uid":14722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"事緣今日去左一個叫拉差達火車夜市嘅地方 見到間海鮮pad thai 250baht一份 於是我就比1000baht其中一個女人 佢拎左之後就行開左繼續送餐 過左兩三分鐘我同佢講未找錢 佢一開頭話已經找左 後尾仲話我未比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  結果就口同鼻拗 <br />\n之後我打1155搵tourist police 佢地叫我直接報警 但係之前已經聽過泰國警察無咩效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又怕間鋪屈翻我地食霸王餐 於是就咁就走左 我唔知佢係有心呃我定太忙唔記得 但大家如果會去就盡量避免去呢間 或者比完錢要即刻捉住佢找錢<br />\n<br />\n間鋪<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/233010_f4efbd4518bec7e4568c1e3fdbf2696b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F233010_f4efbd4518bec7e4568c1e3fdbf2696b.png&h=568a8093&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dad97f07ddc0e3d5a75472716671435911d83d8","tid":519703,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"咁你有無報到警？咁你有無找番錢？"},{"pid":"39ed64ac375edf14bee7c75507e403db1dfc652a","tid":519703,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dad97f07ddc0e3d5a75472716671435911d83d8","tid":519703,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"咁你有無報到警？咁你有無找番錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:41:56.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n你最後走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871ebccf7dd88a3d5e4d425e84ee22d5124fc4e1","tid":519703,"uid":14722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ed64ac375edf14bee7c75507e403db1dfc652a","tid":519703,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dad97f07ddc0e3d5a7547